des:
OzoLife is a smart device management App for you to control and manage digital locks, P2P cameras, DOORBELL and other smart products from Ozone Brand. With OzoLife, users can:
1. Remotely control smart locks and OTHER SECURITY DEVICES from anywhere.
2. Add and control multiple devices at once with one App.
3. Easily share devices among family members.

(1) Download our “OzoLife” app from Google Play / App Store then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our “OzoLife” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, IOS or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “OzoLife” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “OzoLife” skill, and you'll be navigated to “OzoLife” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, lock the front door.
Alexa, unlock the front door.
Alexa, is the front door unlocked?
Alexa, show me the front door.
Alexa, show me the backyard.
Alexa, is the window open?
